						<p class="text-gray-700 text-sm">Not demo pages or placeholders. Example tests: pet supply e-commerce store (24 products), photography portfolio (47 images), SaaS landing page with pricing, restaurant site with online menu. If I can't launch it, it doesn't work.</p>
					</div>

					<div class="border-[3px] border-gray-200 p-5">
						<h3 class="text-lg font-black text-gray-900 mb-3">üé® Test Design Quality</h3>
						<p class="text-gray-700 text-sm">Compare AI output to professional design benchmarks: typography hierarchy, spacing consistency, color harmony, visual polish. Framer generates portfolio-worthy designs in 2 minutes. Wix generates 2010-era generic templates. Both tested, both scored accordingly.</p>
					</div>

					<div class="border-[3px] border-gray-200 p-5">
